This is a meta-package containing standard packages that can be included in almost every LaTeX document with some mathematics inside.

A list of these packages is

* hyperref
* xcolor
* amsmath, amssymb amsthm
* tikz
* mathtools
* etoolbox
* xparse

In draft mode, the following are also loaded:
* todonotes
* showkeys

Some extra useful packages are:
* datetime
* watermark (optional)
* biblatex (optional)

Moreover, these packages are loaded with sensible defaults.